资讯科技硬件与设备</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">2.9</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">小米集团－Ｗ</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(01810)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">49（1.2%）</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">金属与采矿</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">1.8</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">中国宏桥</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(01378)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">12.62（3.4%）</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">医疗保健设备与服务</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">1</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">京东健康</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(06618)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">35.2（-1.5%）</td></tr></table></div>",
